title: [Firefly Villa, Corridor]
description: White stucco walls line the northern side of the corridor and stand opposite ornate windows of stained glass.  A myriad of hues swirls through the colored panes to bathe a paneled mahogany door and a golden linden door in their sun-warmed light.

White stucco walls line the northern side of the corridor and stand opposite ornate windows of stained glass.  As moonlight filters through the panes, it bathes a paneled mahogany door and a golden linden door in its silvery glow.
